\f1\b Replication.data.beheadings.march.15.dta
\f2\b0 \
Stata file.\
This is the replication dataset. It consists on monthly panel observations for 2441 municipalities in Mexico from January 1998 to December 2010. Mexico City is considered as a single municipality.\
It contains all the variables used in the econometric specifications presented in the paper. This includes homicides of males between 15 and 39 years old and homicides among the rest of the population; indicator variables for captures and killings of leaders and lieutenants; population; indicator variables for central or strategic municipalities in the transportation network; and indicator variables interacting captures with post-capture time periods (1-6 months, 7-12 months, >12 months).\
\

